{"tid":953443,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾朗自己廢被擋出補射又唔入　躁到狂踢門柱發洩","createTime":"2018-12-24T02:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T14:25:32.000Z","uid":54373,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"28de512da8fd06f1a022b69972215b795d95a7b8","tid":953443,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181223/large/1545552774_3bde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181223%2Flarge%2F1545552774_3bde.jpg&h=fcf670f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母! 我比美斯拋離!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181223/large/1545552780_c825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181223%2Flarge%2F1545552780_c825.jpg&h=e83dae0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母! 我比美斯拋離!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181223/large/1545552783_07c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181223%2Flarge%2F1545552783_07c0.jpg&h=6869793a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母! 我比美斯拋離!</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯周六於主場以1:0小勝羅馬的意甲聯賽，基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）數度攻門都未能射破由門將羅賓奧臣把關的客軍大門，C朗下半場在一次攻門又被羅賓奧臣擋出、補射又未能得手後發𤷪𤺧，不忿得踢門柱發洩。<br />\n<br />\n羅馬的瑞典門將羅賓奧臣周六在對祖記的賽事作出了多次精撲救，包括撲出C朗33分鐘在禁區左路的一次勁射。59分鐘，C朗近門頭槌攻門被羅賓奧臣救出，僅1分鐘後，C朗於門前施射被奧臣擋出，他隨即補射亦失諸交臂後，屢射不入的這名葡萄牙球星結果以腳踢門柱洩憤。"},{"pid":"bcd5dbcbc29a71957454489bbad32fd478f6baa3","tid":953443,"uid":54373,"like":40,"dislike":3,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:00:45.000Z","msg":"本輪數據<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">賤朗 - 10射0入 (仲要得3球中龍 賽後評為最垃圾6.6分)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n美斯- 3射1入 (2中龍)<br />\n<br />\n賤種朗<br />\n聯賽: 119射11入球 (3球靠12碼) (9.24%)<br />\n歐聯: 27射1入球 1紅牌 (3.7%)<br />\n已射146球 得個12個入球 合共8.21%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯<br />\n聯賽: 71射15入球 (1球靠12碼) (21.1%)<br />\n歐聯: 20射6入球 0紅牌 (30%)<br />\n91射入21球 合共23%"},{"pid":"3e761fbecf100a5a813672444f065574ce1927a6","tid":953443,"uid":60092,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:00:48.000Z","msg":"阿朗呢期已經好多嘢煩，放過佢得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8ea6aa5ae38c8cd6595f7b4bc97f317dbe6e18","tid":953443,"uid":54373,"like":69,"dislike":4,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"3e761fbecf100a5a813672444f065574ce1927a6","tid":953443,"uid":60092,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:00:48.000Z","msg":"阿朗呢期已經好多嘢煩，放過佢得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:02:30.000Z","msg":"放過佢?<br />\n邊個放過廣大女人既後門<br />\n邊個放過清潔呀姐幫佢清潔佢隨地柯尿D尿跡"},{"pid":"8a937f9d7f853db0f00fbe022eaef6294c1a8b73","tid":953443,"uid":1560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4194463b015927657f00e61b4fc910126ebda40d","tid":953443,"uid":58811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ae8ea6aa5ae38c8cd6595f7b4bc97f317dbe6e18","tid":953443,"uid":54373,"like":69,"dislike":4,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"3e761fbecf100a5a813672444f065574ce1927a6","tid":953443,"uid":60092,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:00:48.000Z","msg":"阿朗呢期已經好多嘢煩，放過佢得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c